comments.content: Sure looks like a variation of House Chalet Comprimé, but I could be very wrong.

Then again, [I could be right](http://web.archive.org/web/20071211201130/http:/www.houseind.com/index.php?page=showfont&id=11&subpage=viewfonts).

Yes, I know, I realize I sound like [a PIL song](http://web.archive.org/web/20071211201130/http:/www.stlyrics.com/songs/p/pil7083/rise553998.html).
